---
title: Kafka Event Flow — Successful Certification Path
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor CoopAdmin as Cooperative Admin
    participant CM as CooperativeModule
    participant PM as ProductModule
    participant CertM as CertificationModule
    participant NM as NotificationModule
    participant K as Kafka (Redpanda)

    CoopAdmin->>CM: Register cooperative (CIN/ICE/IF)
    CM->>K: cooperative.registration.submitted
    K->>NM: cooperative.registration.submitted
    NM-->>CoopAdmin: Email: Registration received

    Note over CM: super-admin verifies
    CM->>K: cooperative.registration.verified
    K->>CertM: cooperative.registration.verified (read model)
    K->>PM: cooperative.registration.verified (read model)

    CoopAdmin->>PM: Log harvest + create batch
    PM->>K: product.batch.created

    Note over PM: Lab technician submits test results
    PM->>K: lab.test.completed (passed: true)
    K->>CertM: lab.test.completed → update batch eligibility
    K->>NM: lab.test.completed
    NM-->>CoopAdmin: Email: Lab results (passed)

    CoopAdmin->>CertM: POST /certifications/request
    CertM->>K: certification.requested
    K->>NM: certification.requested
    NM-->>CoopAdmin: Email: Certification request received

    Note over CertM: certification-body schedules inspection
    CertM->>K: certification.inspection.scheduled
    K->>NM: certification.inspection.scheduled
    NM-->>CoopAdmin: Email: Inspection scheduled

    Note over CertM: inspector files passing report
    CertM->>K: certification.inspection.completed

    Note over CertM: certification-body grants
    CertM->>K: certification.decision.granted
    K->>NM: certification.decision.granted
    NM-->>CoopAdmin: Email: 🎉 Certification TERROIR-AOP-SFI-2025-001 granted

    CoopAdmin->>CertM: POST /qr-codes/{certificationId}
    CertM->>K: certification.qrcode.generated
